data.description: Location!!! Location!!! Location!!!! Centrally located well-maintained ranch home move-in ready. Close to Downtown, Coconut Grove, Key Biscayne, and Miami Airport. Tremendous potential to easily add a 3rd and 4th bedroom with an additional bathroom. Screened-in porch and nice yard with plenty of room for a pool. Close to schools, shops and restaurants.
